<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">How to Use Remindly</h1>
  
  <!-- Introduction -->
  <div class="bg-white shadow rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
      Welcome to Remindly! This guide will help you understand the main features of our application and show you how to get started.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Main Functionalities -->
  <div class="space-y-8 mb-12">
    <!-- Reminders Section -->
    <div class="bg-white shadow rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="flex items-start mb-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 17h5l-1.405-1.405A2.032 2.032 0 0118 14.158V11a6.002 6.002 0 00-4-5.659V5a2 2 0 10-4 0v.341C7.67 6.165 6 8.388 6 11v3.159c0 .538-.214 1.055-.595 1.436L4 17h5m6 0v1a3 3 0 11-6 0v-1m6 0H9"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="ml-4 flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Reminders</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Reminders help seniors stay on track with their daily routines and important activities. Caregivers can set up recurring reminders for medications, meals, appointments, and other essential tasks. Each reminder can be customized with:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li><strong>Custom schedules:</strong> Daily, weekly, or custom frequencies</li>
            <li><strong>Specific times:</strong> Set exact times for each reminder</li>
            <li><strong>Categories:</strong> Organize by medication, meal, appointment, or routine</li>
            <li><strong>Voice announcements:</strong> Seniors receive spoken reminders on their devices</li>
            <li><strong>Acknowledgment tracking:</strong> Care receivers can acknowledge reminders or snooze them, and caregivers can see which reminders were completed</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tasks Section -->
    <div class="bg-white shadow rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="flex items-start mb-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="ml-4 flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Tasks</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Tasks enable caregivers to coordinate care activities and manage one-time or scheduled responsibilities. Unlike reminders that repeat regularly, tasks are specific activities that need to be completed. Features include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li><strong>Task assignment:</strong> Assign tasks to specific caregivers or leave them unassigned</li>
            <li><strong>Scheduling:</strong> Set due dates and times for tasks</li>
            <li><strong>Priority levels:</strong> Mark tasks as low, medium, or high priority</li>
            <li><strong>Comments:</strong> Caregivers can add notes and updates on task progress</li>
            <li><strong>Visibility control:</strong> Choose whether seniors can see specific tasks</li>
            <li><strong>Status tracking:</strong> Monitor pending, in-progress, and completed tasks</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Video Tutorials -->
  <div class="bg-white shadow rounded-lg p-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Video Tutorials</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
      Watch these short video guides to learn how to use Remindly:
    </p>
    
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <!-- Video 1: Login -->
      <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How to Log In (No password needed)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
          Learn how to access Remindly using our secure magic link authentication - no passwords to remember!
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.loom.com/share/5c8f13372dcb46d0a3eecd19a222cb74" 
           target="_blank" 
           rel="noopener noreferrer"
           class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500">
          <svg class="mr-2 h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM9.555 7.168A1 1 0 008 8v4a1 1 0 001.555.832l3-2a1 1 0 000-1.664l-3-2z"></path>
          </svg>
          Watch Video
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Video 2: Senior Request -->
      <div class="border-l-4 border-green-500 pl-4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How a Senior starts a request to connect with a Caregiver</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
          See how seniors can initiate a connection request to link with their caregivers.
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.loom.com/share/64e21a285d3848deb4e919fe46357221" 
           target="_blank" 
           rel="noopener noreferrer"
           class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-green-500">
          <svg class="mr-2 h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM9.555 7.168A1 1 0 008 8v4a1 1 0 001.555.832l3-2a1 1 0 000-1.664l-3-2z"></path>
          </svg>
          Watch Video
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Video 3: Caregiver Connect -->
      <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How a Caregiver connects with a Senior</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
          Learn the steps for caregivers to accept connection requests and start managing care.
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.loom.com/share/c76db493295b4235a3703fff4ce20275" 
           target="_blank" 
           rel="noopener noreferrer"
           class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-purple-500">
          <svg class="mr-2 h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM9.555 7.168A1 1 0 008 8v4a1 1 0 001.555.832l3-2a1 1 0 000-1.664l-3-2z"></path>
          </svg>
          Watch Video
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Back Navigation -->
  <div class="mt-8 text-center">
    <% if current_user %>
      <%= link_to "Back to Dashboard", dashboard_path, class: "inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-gray-300 shadow-sm text-base font-medium rounded-md text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500" %>
    <% else %>
      <%= link_to "Back to Login", login_path, class: "inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-gray-300 shadow-sm text-base font-medium rounded-md text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500" %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Version Info -->
  <div class="mt-6 text-center">
    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">v<%= APP_VERSION %></span>
  </div>
</div>
